Cook pasta according to package directions; drain. Meanwhile, cook Johnsonville(R) Mild Italian Ground Sausage in a 10-inch nonstick skillet until meat is brown; drain. Set meat aside. Wipe skillet with paper towel. Spread about half of the cooked pasta in the skillet. Cover with about half of the Classico(R) Tomato and Basil pasta sauce. Spoon cooked meat over Classico(R) Tomato and Basil pasta sauce. Sprinkle with 1 cup of the mozzarella cheese. Top with remaining pasta and sauce. Sprinkle remaining mozzarella and Parmesan cheese over top. Cook, covered, over medium heat for 5 to 7 minutes or until heated through and cheese melts. Remove skillet from heat and let stand, covered, for 1 minute.